                <project id="10100" key="JDK">JDK</project>
                    <description>Try to recover and output meaningful information in more situations, such as:&lt;br/&gt;
- when a pointer is in Method metadata memory range, but the memory is not committed&lt;br/&gt;
- when we call a bad address&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
