                            <comment id="14718200" author="mbaesken" created="Thu, 31 Oct 2024 01:38:05 -0700"  >Thanks [~dlong] for confirming.  I created &lt;a href=&quot;https://bugs.openjdk.org/browse/JDK-8343343&quot; title=&quot;Misc crash dump improvements on more platforms after JDK-8294160&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;JDK-8343343&quot;&gt;&lt;strike&gt;JDK-8343343&lt;/strike&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to add support on more platforms.&lt;br/&gt;
